Author: Kampy

Email: Kampy20@gmx.de

website: www.kampys-stuff.de


=======================================
LEVEL DESCRIPTION: 

Remake of my popular Counter-Strike 1.6 map "cs_fat_mansion". 
This is a cs_mansion type of map, but smaller and with more
ways to move for the CT-team.

=======================================================
INSTALLATION:

The game files are:

cs_fat_mansion.bsp
cs_fat_mansion.nav

Place both files in your cstrike\maps folder, typically:

C:\Program files\Steam\SteamApps\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps\

=======================================================
BETA TESTERS:

Einhander
Cozmicshredder
Killroy

and some others
thank you guys ;-)
